about.summary: Tools for the comparison of distributions. This includes nonparametric estimation of the relative distribution PDF and CDF and numerical summaries as described in "Relative Distribution Methods in the Social Sciences" by Mark S. Handcock and Martina Morris, Springer-Verlag, 1999, Springer-Verlag, ISBN 0387987789.

name: r-reldist
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.6-6' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-reldist
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/reldist_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/reldist/reldist_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8a7b55120d24fae72b4c284072b07d7f90094ba00bf89ba172e0b3ab8fbe7127

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 2
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-hmisc
    - r-mgcv
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-hmisc
    - r-mgcv

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('reldist')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('reldist')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://www.stat.ucla.edu/~handcock/RelDist
  license: GPL-3
  summary: Tools for the comparison of distributions. This includes nonparametric estimation
    of the relative distribution PDF and CDF and numerical summaries as described in
    "Relative Distribution Methods in the Social Sciences" by Mark S. Handcock and Martina
    Morris, Springer-Verlag, 1999, Springer-Verlag, ISBN 0387987789.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r

Handcock and Martina Morris, Springer-Verlag, 1999, Springer-Verlag, ISBN 0387987789.
